	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just a question to clarify a single point in this otherwise quite enlightening post.&nbsp;&nbsp;Mentioning having "Access to (IMO) the best cleric quest item in the game", is referring to the Regent Symbol of Innoruuk for the Engulfing Darkness spell?  I must confess that I am most anxious to prove myself worthy of this item, both for the spell and the armour and +WIS bonus.  If this was not the quest item you refer to, please educate an eager young acolyte.  *smiles*<br><br>Also, it's worth noting that we Teir'Dal also have the hide skill (as well as the toelings *wink*).  Finding a shady spot to rest *grins*, hiding, and conning even something so weak as a Fire Beetle gives us some assurance of our success, and makes meditating in the wilds a more comfortable prospect.<br><br>Avallach (9th level Priest of Innoruuk) Cazic-Thule<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
